OL,3,COlympic ice skating legends Torvill
OL,4,Cand Dean receive honours from King
OL,6,FLegendary ice skaters Jayne Torvill
OL,7,Fand Christopher Dean have been
OL,8,Fhonoured for their services to ice
OL,9,Fskating and voluntary service at a
OL,10,Fspecial ceremony at Windsor Castle.
OL,12,FThe pair from Nottingham famously won
OL,13,Fgold for Great Britain with their
OL,14,Fperformance of Bolero at the 1984
OL,15,FWinter Olympics.
OL,17,FTheir legacy is permanently recognised
OL,18,Fin the city through several landmarks
OL,19,Fand honours, including Bolero Square
OL,20,Fand with the Torvill and Dean Rink at
OL,21,Fthe National Ice Centre.
OL,26,@vD@Srr
