PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780531377
OL,3,COlympic ice skating legends Torvill
OL,4,Cand Dean receive honours from King
OL,6,FNow Jayne Torvill has been appointed a
OL,7,Fdame, while Christopher Dean has been
OL,8,Fknighted in the King's New Year
OL,9,FHonours List.
OL,11,FThey were among 68 people to receive
OL,12,Fawards from the King on Tuesday,
OL,13,Falongside Luther star Sir Idris Elba
OL,14,Fand comedian and actress Dame Meera
OL,15,FSyal.
OL,17,FSpeaking at the ceremony, Mr Dean
OL,18,Fopened up about what it meant to
OL,19,Fbecome a sir.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780531377
OL,3,COlympic ice skating legends Torvill
OL,4,Cand Dean receive honours from King
OL,6,FHe said: "When you say it, it sounds
OL,7,Freally nice actually. Really honoured
OL,8,Fto receive the awards today. It was
OL,9,Fsuch a special day.
OL,11,F"We met the King, he asked us what we
OL,12,Fwere doing now and we said we were
OL,13,Fretired and we did recommend it to him.
OL,15,F"I'm still doing a bit of choreography
OL,16,Fhere and there, so i'm keeping my feet
OL,17,Fin shall we say and the skates were on
OL,18,Fabout two weeks ago in Italy doing a
OL,19,Fbit of work. they still go on but they
OL,20,Fgo on rarely."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780531377
OL,3,COlympic ice skating legends Torvill
OL,4,Cand Dean receive honours from King
OL,6,FJayne said: "It was lovely to meet the
OL,7,FKing again and we had a little chat,
OL,8,Fhe made us feel really comfortable."
OL,10,FAsked about their conversations with
OL,11,FCharles, Dame Jayne said he asked
OL,12,Fwhether they were still skating and
OL,13,Ftold her he was "so pleased" to
OL,14,Frecognise their achievements.
OL,16,FShe said: "He said 'Are you coaching
OL,17,For anything?', and I said 'no, we've
OL,18,Fjust retired now'. We did our last
OL,19,Ftour last year, and that the body was
OL,20,Fdeciding that that was our last tour,
OL,21,Fbut we enjoyed it."
OL,26,@uD@QOUuD@\O]xD@KOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
