OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780531377
OL,3,COlympic ice skating legends Torvill
OL,4,Cand Dean receive honours from King
OL,6,FSir Christopher said: "I had a similar
OL,7,Fconversation. I also said: 'We've
OL,8,Fretired, and I recommend it', and he
OL,9,Fhad a little laugh."
OL,11,FNews of their damehood and knighthood
OL,12,Farrived at the end of a year in which
OL,13,Fthe pair retired from performing after
OL,14,Ftheir UK "farewell" tour, which
OL,15,Fculminated in their home city of
OL,16,FNottingham in July.
OL,26,@nD@WOUqD@TO]vD@JOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
