OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780531377
OL,3,COlympic ice skating legends Torvill
OL,4,Cand Dean receive honours from King
OL,6,FAsked what it was like to step off the
OL,7,Fice for the final time together, Dame
OL,8,FJayne, 68, said: "It was a mixture of
OL,9,Femotions, but we were so happy to have
OL,10,Fbeen able to do that tour, and you
OL,11,Falways want to give a good
OL,12,Fperformance, and we felt that that
OL,13,Fshow as a whole was one of the best
OL,14,Fperformances."
OL,26,@pD@ROUvD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780531377
OL,3,COlympic ice skating legends Torvill
OL,4,Cand Dean receive honours from King
OL,6,F"And we prepared ourselves for that,"
OL,7,FSir Christopher, 67, added. "To put a
OL,8,Ftour like that together takes about a
OL,9,Fyear and a half, and so that
OL,10,Fpreparation is always in the back of
OL,11,Fyour mind that this is the final
OL,12,Fperformance.
OL,14,F"A lot of people say, 'won't you miss
OL,15,Fit?', but we feel like we've achieved
OL,16,Fwhat we've achieved, and we don't need
OL,17,Fto do any more. The body doesn't want
OL,18,Fto do any more. And so, for us to be
OL,19,Fable to do that in a style that we
OL,20,Ffelt was fitting for us, it was great."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@eO]oD@]OUvD@AOU|D@gO]
