OL,3,COlympic ice skating legends Torvill
OL,4,Cand Dean receive honours from King
OL,6,FDame Jayne found out about her
OL,7,Fdamehood around three days before her
OL,8,Fdance partner ` realising he had not
OL,9,Fyet received a letter when she phoned
OL,10,Fhim to celebrate the news.
OL,12,FSir Christopher added: "I wanted to
OL,13,Fbe, and was, happy for Jayne, but at
OL,14,Fthe same time ` and Jayne felt the
OL,15,Fsame as well ` that you didn't know
OL,16,Fhow to act, neither of us did, did we?"
OL,26,@tD@XOUxD@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
